    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Slice your <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> (skins on) into 1-2cm thick discs</p><p>Add your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> to a large pot of<strong> boiled water </strong>and bring to a boil over a high heat</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/wholewheat-pasta-alla-genovese/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>potato discs</strong> to the pot and cook for an initial 4 min</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/wholewheat-pasta-alla-genovese/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are cooking, chop most of your <strong>basil</strong> roughly, including the stalks (save some leaves for garnish!)</p><p>Peel and chop your <strong>garlic</strong> roughly</p><p>Trim your <strong>green beans</strong>, then chop them in half</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/wholewheat-pasta-alla-genovese/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>pasta</strong> to the pot and cook for a further 7-9 min (10-12 min for wholewheat)</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/wholewheat-pasta-alla-genovese/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Whilst the potatoes & pasta are cooking, add the <strong>chopped basil</strong> and <strong>garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) to a <strong>food processor</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>cashew nuts</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>flaked almonds</strong> (save the rest for garnish!), 70ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[105ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[140ml]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, 1/2 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><span class=\"text-purple\">[3/4 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp]</span><strong> salt</strong> and a very generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Blitz until very smooth \u2013 this is your <strong>basil</strong> <strong>pesto</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/wholewheat-pasta-alla-genovese/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped green beans</strong> to the potatoes & pasta and cook for a further 5 min or until everything is cooked</p><p>Once cooked, drain the <strong>potatoes, green beans & pasta</strong></p><p>Return everything to the pot</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/wholewheat-pasta-alla-genovese/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>basil</strong> <strong>pesto</strong> to the pot and give everything a good mix up \u2013 this is your <strong>pasta alla genovese</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/wholewheat-pasta-alla-genovese/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>pasta alla genovese</strong> and garnish with the <strong>reserved basil leaves </strong>and<strong> flaked almonds</strong></p><p>Drizzle with some <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
